    FieldVisibility - Bugzilla extension

FieldVisibility is a very simply extension to Bugzilla at the moment. It just lets You to show / hide a few parts from a bug based on severity. This parts are:

 - Verion
 - Platform
 - Target Milestone
 - URL
 - WhiteBoard
 - KeyWords
 - Frequency
 - Operator

.

    INSTALLATION

Install extension by extracting files from archive. Switch to 'extension' directory below Bugzilla root directory and extract files from archive.


